caption: Food is great! Fresh and they are very quick to put all your order ready. They offer a variety of salads, wraps, sandwiches and bowls with vegetarian options and low fat drinks/ snacks.  It also has a beautiful area to sit and stay there …

I have eaten here a few times for both breakfast and lunch. Every time the food is fresh and delicious! My co-workers have complained about the price of the food being too high, but I think it’s worth every penny because it’s good food made fresh everyday and convenient not having to leave the office building to find food. Thanks Kim!

this place is very highly priced. I ordered 1 slice of toast and I was charged $ 2.69 (noted on receipt as price of taco)... this is horrible. This is not the first time that I have ordered just a slice of toast and get charged various prices.
